This week's deal appeared in ^*BThe Bridge Magicians^*N, a recent new book by ^*BMark Horton^*N and ^*BRadolaw Kielbasinski^*N. This book was published by our friends at ^*BMaster Point Press^*N, a Canadian company that, despite its young age, has established itself as one of the premier bridge publishing companies in the world. You can find out more about the many fine books that ^*BMaster Point Press^*N has published through their web site. Click on the yellow rectangle below to be taken directly to this web site in a new browser window.

